Package org.gicentre.tests

Test classes to check TreeMappa is behaving correctly.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    TreeMapFromCodeTest
    Creates a treemap programmatically.
    TreeMapProcessingTest
    Tests the Processing wrapper for the treeMappa classes.
    TreeMLTest
    Tests reading a TreeML format file and creating a deep, unbalanced treemap.

Package org.gicentre.tests Description

Test classes to check TreeMappa is behaving correctly.

This package contains test classes. These should not be included in the distribution, but are useful for checking TreeMappa is behaving correctly.
